1.Change file on the VM /etc/ssh/sshd_config
         PermitRootLogin yes
2.start Terminal.app
3.right click New remote connection
4. '+' add server and choose it
5. type 'User:' root
6. connect
7. adduser new_user
8. exit
9. type 'User:' new_user
10. connect

////With ssh session////
1.change file on the VM /etc/ssh/sshd_config
         PermitRootLogin yes
2.ssh root@address
3.adduser new_user
4.exit root@address
5.connect new_user@address
